{"article_id":"J47FHrb05ASltq8g","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In the wake of the 2016 election , Facebook had a problem .","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"A lot of people thought","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"the site had done too little","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to combat fake news .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"At the same time , Facebook was desperate to maintain its reputation as a politically innocuous technology company .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"If it started directly declaring certain news stories fake ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"it would inevitably be drawn into emotionally charged political fights ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"damaging its credibility with partisans in the process .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"So","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"instead of trying to identify fake news itself ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Facebook is outsourcing the work to third parties .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Initially , five fact-checking organizations","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"- Snopes , PolitiFact , Factcheck.org , ABC News , and the Associated Press -","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"will be asked to review questionable articles","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"and render a verdict about their veracity .","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"If an article is rated false by these organizations ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"it will be marked as \" disputed \"","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"and be pushed lower in a user ' s newsfeed .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"That puts some distance between Facebook and the politically charged question of what counts as fake news .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"But it ' s not clear if this will be sufficient","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"to mollify critics","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"- predominantly on the right -","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"who object to the very concept","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"of trying to weed fake news out of the newsfeed .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"At the same time , Facebook is giving fact-checking organizations a kind of power","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"they ' ve never had before :","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"the power","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"to publicly brand other websites ' stories as \" disputed \"","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"and push them down in Facebook users ' newsfeeds .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Facebook ' s new fact-checking system is going to subject these organizations","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"- some of them quite small -","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"to an unprecedented amount of public scrutiny .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"The problem is that","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"- especially in the middle of a political campaign -","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"what ' s a \" fact \" is often hotly disputed .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"\" PolitiFact consistently calls Republicans liars at two or three times the rate of Democrats , \"","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"wrote Mark Hemingway in the conservative Weekly Standard in 2013 .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"\" Its individual judgments are regularly erroneous in ways","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that make it hard not to suspect","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"the organization has a serious problem with political bias. \"","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"In a Friday piece","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"reacting to Facebook ' s announcement ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Hemingway wrote","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"that PolitiFact \" might well be the most biased news organization in America . \"","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Of course , fact-checking organizations deny","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"that they ' re biased .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"\" Our challenge to folks","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"who say","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"PolitiFact is biased","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"is :","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"' Give me examples , ' \"","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"says Aaron Sharockman of PolitiFact , a fact-checking group","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"associated with the Tampa Bay Times .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"\" Often we get a lot of silence back . \"","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"But PolitiFact ' s conservative critics say","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"they ' re happy to supply examples of apparent bias .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"In a recent critique of fact-checking websites at Current Affairs , Nathan Robinson pointed out a case","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"where PolitiFact had rated as \" mostly false \" Donald Trump ' s claim","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"that \" windmills are killing hundreds and hundreds of eagles. \"","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"PolitiFact interpreted this as a claim","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that windmills are killing hundreds of eagles per year ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"which is probably false .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"as Robinson points out ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Trump didn ' t say \" per year , \"","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"and over multiple years windmills almost certainly have killed hundreds of eagles .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"And PolitiFact ' s nitpicking of Trump ' s statements contrasts with the more generous attitude","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"it sometimes takes toward the statements of other politicians .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"For example , PolitiFact rated as \" mostly false \" Donald Trump ' s claim","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that the real unemployment rate among black people ages 18 to 24 was 59 percent .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Trump was likely referring to the fact","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"that the employment-to-population ratio for black youths was 41 percent ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"leaving 59 percent outside the workforce .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"But that ' s a different figure from the unemployment rate .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Yet","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"when Bernie Sanders made a very similar mistake a year earlier ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"claiming","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"that the \" real unemployment rate \" among teens ages 17 to 20 was 51 percent ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"PolitiFact rated this \" mostly true. \"","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"True , Sanders was using the wrong terminology ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"it said ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"but the larger point","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"Sanders was making","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"was basically true :","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Young black people were having more trouble finding work than young white people .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"This , of course , was also the point","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Trump tried to make a year later ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"but PolitiFact was not in such a forgiving mood","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"when he made this particular gaffe .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"\" Critics point to one or two or three or even 10 statements over a nine-year span , \"","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"Sharockman says ,","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"but he points out","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"that his organization has conducted more than 13,000 fact-checks in its history .","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"He argues","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"that the isolated examples","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"conservatives like to cite","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"don ' t reflect the organization ' s larger body of work .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"Sharockman also says","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"that PolitiFact ' s critics are not limited to the right .","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"Liberal cable TV host Rachel Maddow has devoted several segments to blasting the organization for what she views as mistakes .","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"For example , PolitiFact initially rated Marco Rubio ' s claim","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"that most Americans are conservative","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"\" mostly true ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"\"","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"even though most polls show","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"that a mere plurality","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"- but not a majority -","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"of voters describe themselves that way .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"Maddow thinks","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"the claim should have been rated false -","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"PolitiFact eventually modified its rating to \" half true . \"","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"\" People on the edges of a particular ideology","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"- I think","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"this applies in both directions -","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"they see the world in much starker terms","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"than PolitiFact does , \"","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"Sharockman says .","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"\" For a lot of really partisan conservatives , and for progressive liberals , they see things as true and false","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"and do n't believe","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"there are shades of gray in between . \"","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"Of the fact-checking groups","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"selected by Facebook ,","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"PolitiFact is the one","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"that has drawn the most ire from conservatives .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"This may be because its mission","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"of vetting the statements of candidates for office","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"regularly puts it in the middle of partisan political disputes .","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"Factcheck.org has a mission similar to PolitiFact ' s","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"but has not drawn as much conservative criticism .","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"Another Facebook-selected group , Snopes , is more focused on debunking urban legends and bogus email forwards","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"- sometimes , but not always , about politics .","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"The final two groups , the AP and ABC News , are conventional news organizations .","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"The optimistic case for Facebook ' s fact-checking project is that identifying fake news is an easier and less politically fraught problem","depth":5},{"id":133,"text":"than determining when politicians are lying .","depth":5},{"id":134,"text":"A common problem for fact-checkers is that their calls are often tied up with the merits of the underlying issues","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"candidates are arguing about .","depth":6},{"id":136,"text":"In a 2012 piece , for example , Hemingway faulted PolitiFact","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"for giving Mitt Romney a \" pants on fire \" rating","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"for claiming","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"that Obama was planning to gut the work requirements of the 1996 welfare reform law .","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"Unsurprisingly , a conservative expert thought","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"Romney ' s characterization of Obama ' s proposal was fair game ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"while more liberal experts thought","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"Romney ' s criticism was unfair .","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"It might seem like identifying fake news","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"- at least the kind","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"that ' s made up out of whole cloth -","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"would be more straightforward .","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"if you dig a little deeper into real fake-news controversies ,","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"you quickly find","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"that distinguishing real stories from fake ones can require the same kinds of subjective judgment calls","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"required to distinguish between politicians ' truthful statements and their lies .","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"Consider , for example , BuzzFeed ' s list of the five biggest fake news stories in the three months before the election .","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"The top story ,","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"Pope Francis","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"endorsing Donald Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"is obviously fake .","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"But the second and third stories claim","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"that WikiLeaks emails show Hillary Clinton selling weapons to ISIS ,","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"and here the verdict isn ' t so clear .","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"Snopes examined this claim","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"and found","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"that it contained a \" mixture \" of true and false claims .","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"There is zero evidence","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"that Clinton directly and knowingly sold weapons to ISIS ,","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"Snopes concluded .","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"But WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange has claimed","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"that leaked documents show Clinton ' s State Department selling weapons to militants in Libya ,","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"some of which ultimately ended up in the hands of ISIS fighters .","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"Assange ' s evidence for this claim seems flimsy .","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"But this doesn ' t seem like \" fake news \" in the sense","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"of being deliberately made up .","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"Whoever wrote that story may have really believed","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"that Clinton ' s policies led to ISIS fighters getting US weapons .","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"Another story","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"that was widely branded as fake news","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"claimed","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"that Pepsi CEO Indra Nooyi told Trump supporters to \" take their business elsewhere \" a few days after the election .","depth":6},{"id":179,"text":"Nooyi never actually said those words .","depth":7},{"id":180,"text":"But she did make comments","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"expressing dismay at Trump ' s election -","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"comments","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"that conservative sites quickly reported on .","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"In a newsgathering game of telephone , one publication paraphrased Nooyi","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"as telling people to take their business elsewhere ,","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"which others then misinterpreted as a direct quotation .","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"Snopes rated this \" mostly false \"","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"but acknowledged","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"it wasn ' t completely false -","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"Pepsi ' s CEO really had made negative comments about Trump ' s election .","depth":9},{"id":191,"text":"And it ' s not obvious that anyone was trying to be deceptive here ;","depth":7},{"id":192,"text":"it was just extremely sloppy journalism .","depth":7},{"id":193,"text":"When they evaluate articles for Facebook ,","depth":6},{"id":194,"text":"these organizations won ' t have a \" half true \" or \" mostly false \" option .","depth":6},{"id":195,"text":"They ' re going to have to decide which news stories to rate as fake","depth":7},{"id":196,"text":"- thereby branding them as \" disputed \" in the Facebook newsfeed -","depth":7},{"id":197,"text":"and which ones to leave alone .","depth":6},{"id":198,"text":"Sharockman says","depth":7},{"id":199,"text":"PolitiFact plans to be very conservative about this .","depth":7},{"id":200,"text":"\" We 're looking for clear calls , \"","depth":10},{"id":201,"text":"he says .","depth":10},{"id":202,"text":"\" We 're going to look for things","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"that we think","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"are not close. \"","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"If an article has shades of gray ,","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"he says ,","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"PolitiFact will skip it .","depth":9},{"id":208,"text":"But of course , what looks like a shade of gray to one person might look like a clear falsehood to others .","depth":7},{"id":209,"text":"No matter what PolitiFact and other fact-checking organizations do ,","depth":6},{"id":210,"text":"they ' re likely to make someone unhappy .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":421,"left":330,"right":420,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":330,"left":299,"right":329,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":254,"right":298,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":218,"right":253,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":218,"left":214,"right":217,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":214,"left":0,"right":213,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":213,"left":1,"right":212,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":212,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":4,"right":216,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":216,"left":5,"right":215,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":215,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":238,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":233,"right":237,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":233,"left":220,"right":232,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":220,"left":8,"right":219,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":219,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":232,"left":226,"right":231,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":226,"left":223,"right":225,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":223,"left":221,"right":222,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":221,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":225,"left":15,"right":224,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":224,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":231,"left":18,"right":230,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":230,"left":19,"right":229,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":229,"left":227,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":22,"right":23,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":234,"right":236,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":26,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":27,"right":28,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":252,"left":240,"right":251,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":239,"right":31,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":247,"right":250,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":247,"left":242,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":241,"right":34,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":241,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":243,"right":245,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":243,"left":35,"right":36,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":37,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":38,"right":39,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":250,"left":249,"right":43,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":249,"left":248,"right":42,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":248,"left":40,"right":41,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":275,"right":297,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":263,"right":274,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":263,"left":255,"right":262,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":44,"right":45,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":261,"right":53,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":259,"right":260,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":257,"right":258,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":257,"left":46,"right":256,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":258,"left":49,"right":50,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":260,"left":51,"right":52,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":264,"right":273,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":54,"right":55,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":273,"left":266,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":56,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":57,"right":58,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":268,"right":271,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":268,"left":267,"right":61,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":59,"right":60,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":270,"right":65,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":62,"right":269,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":269,"left":63,"right":64,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":297,"left":276,"right":296,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":66,"right":67,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":292,"right":295,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":286,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":281,"right":285,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":281,"left":277,"right":280,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":68,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":279,"right":73,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":279,"left":70,"right":278,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":71,"right":72,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":284,"right":78,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":284,"left":74,"right":283,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":283,"left":75,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":76,"right":77,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":291,"left":287,"right":290,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":287,"left":79,"right":80,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":289,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":288,"right":83,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":288,"left":81,"right":82,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":293,"right":294,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":293,"left":85,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":87,"right":88,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":329,"left":306,"right":328,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":306,"left":302,"right":305,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":300,"right":301,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":300,"left":89,"right":90,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":91,"right":92,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":305,"left":93,"right":304,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":304,"left":303,"right":96,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":303,"left":94,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":328,"left":307,"right":327,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":307,"left":97,"right":98,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":327,"left":318,